Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:02.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Soon it will be Conan's 10th Anniversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.49,0:00:04.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Overcome one and begin the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A mysterious old couple is living in a new house...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:07.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is this strange feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:09.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is their target me or Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:13.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:19.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, did you see that new\Nhouse for rent in your neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,New house?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of house is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it big?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's small but it's a really beautiful house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You like those types of houses, don't you, Yoshida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I get married, I want live in that kind of house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Married!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, do you want to see it on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, how about just we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's leave those guys alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you calling Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing. It just seemed like someone was watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,THE HOME OF BEIKA'S GRENIER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:03:59.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:07.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Jees, you've already finished eating, Genta{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't get to imaginative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that it's small and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of houses do you like, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking Cohan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, if he's the one that becomes my husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to know what he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's have a look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as you heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we look inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quit joking around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't listened to a word any of you all said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl's father is looking for a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she likes it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first floor has two six-tatami mat rooms,\Na washroom, and a bathroom with a toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess these rooms are usually used for children?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The architecture of this home is\Naimed at couples in their thirties...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the design being based on an image\Nof two children and a family of four.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the second floor, we have a living\Nroom and kitchen with sixteen mats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lighting is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Across the corridor, we have a room of eight mats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there also a third floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this house is special due to its grenier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is really interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a window in here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the evening, you can see the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The detective agency...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You can see it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The grenier and the second floor's living room are great, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rooms on the first floor both seemed a little dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expected more of the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stairs are a little too steep...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, for the amount of space, it's a fair enough deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how about recommending this house to your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "What"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're done looking at the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The layout of the room's wasn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My house's layout is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That house was sold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mom and I were passing by yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a "sold" sign on it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We even asked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's really a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't easy to find a house you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I really didn't like the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need to be sad, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll build you a better house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is it you want to build Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} a house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anyone's going to build it, I'll be the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if those who bought it were\Nin their thirties with two children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that would be just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard it was a grandfather and\Ngrandmother in their seventies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A grandfather and grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That house wasn't designed for older people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stairs are too steep for them, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, everyone has different reasons, so it doesn't matter I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:01.49,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Udohisashi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Udohisashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a strange name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, since the name plate has already been posted...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess they've already moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} would come here to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it's something this small, we must investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the foundation of being a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you kids live in this neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just moved in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would love for you kids to come\Nin and tell me all about this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can leave Beika to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know where to buy delicious eel rice for cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're all detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At Teitan Elementary School,\Nwe're known as the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no one in Beika who doesn't know us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The namesake is almost as famous as mine, Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that the furniture hasn't been delivered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Old Lady, do you and your husband live here together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do the steep stairs not scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've wanted a house like this since I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that feeling well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandmother always says she'd\NLike to live in a high-up apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, I can leave this house\Nto my only son who lives nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you should be careful, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mystery has been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason they bought that house\Nis because their son lives nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She did say that's why they bought that house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there's something they're hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I can't say for certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is it that's making me feel strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:41.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've wanted a house like this since I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's what they're hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But any old man could do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:51.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then, at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why did she make that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow, we won't be back until really\Nlate, so come back and watch the house, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, why're you spacing out and not eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Taxi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi, what are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came at just the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to ask, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you follow that taxi ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those actions aren't unusual for an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it normal for an old man to use a hand to stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I considered that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the old woman being upset with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably because she'd been telling\Nhim to stand up without using his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe so he won't appear so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like when Genta calls me an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:29.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You look like an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can head back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you won't stop until you're satisfied, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is all this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At times like this, I wonder what Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} would do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help you in every way I can, rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any way I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:46.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the end, I had to come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who was that old Chinese guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And just who is that old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:14:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:04.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:06.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The grenier window...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:20.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The window in the grenier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:23.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:24.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why is it directed at the detective agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it to get Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:32.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.47,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.39,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It just seemed like someone was watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is the target me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:40.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could the Black Organization be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it, Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen them in the Organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's possible that they're just disguised...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disguised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disguised, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile, Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor Agasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fell into their trap, Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The professor was on his side this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As revenge for last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should explain me before quizzing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning behind all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, we're here gathering material for Yuusaku's next\Nproject and only arrived in Japan the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:47.85,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Beika, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:49.11,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went home first, but after I got worried about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I went to your primary school to see how you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that exact moment, I saw you and your friends walking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:06.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why are you calling Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really sharp, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd find me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, I was relieved that you were doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I realized I didn't know anything about your new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:28.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to watch Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s daily life after becoming Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I was walking and started thinking,\N"How can I hide so he won't discover me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I then found that house by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it was small, it was just what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to have a look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what was right across from the grenier's window?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The detective agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when she came up with the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We disguised ourselves as an old couple for a week\Nso we could watch your daily life from that window.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even Yuusaku loved my idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, we went to the real estate agent about that house...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only to find out he was a big fan of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:20.91,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He agreed to it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I was surprised when you showed up with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am a former actress, so I knew I could trick you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuusaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's acting is what made me suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not unusual for an old man to use his hands to stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:19:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's usually when there is no one around to see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To show they aren't weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, even in the world of acting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young actors do it when playing older\Npeople, and can ruin plays with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you were upset then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking, "Now you've done it."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a mystery author, not an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, your perception was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You noticed the professor and I were following you, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old Chinese man was the leader of\Nbandits in the mainland in his younger days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was gathering information for the next Night Baron series...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The title of which is Night Baron vs.\NThe Mysterious Man from China."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I was talking with him in a low voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was surprised he threw a sword at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuusaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't you think you overdid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just really worried about your current life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You live so far away from us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you always say you're doing "all right," don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really just wanted to know how it truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:28.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time I saw one of our pictures of the little Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted more of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mom, you never change...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old couple already moved out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we thought, this house isn't suitable for old people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But their name sure was interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:34.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Udohisashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:38.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why didn't I realize it until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.62,0:23:41.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If you read it separately, it's "u-do-ku."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And if you turn "u-do-ku" around...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:46.47,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kudou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:47.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't that right?
